        "name": "Can you do same-day gas safety certificates in Liverpool?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. We offer same-day gas safety certificate appointments across Liverpool and Merseyside. Call us in the morning and we can often complete the inspection and email the certificate the same day." }
