        "name": "What is checked during a gas safety inspection?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Our Gas Safe engineers check all gas appliances including boilers, gas cookers and gas fires. We test for gas leaks, check flue flow and ventilation, verify gas pressure, test safety devices and inspect all pipework and connections. A CP12 certificate is issued if everything passes." }
      },
