    <div class="container">
      <h2>Liverpool Landlord Legal Obligations</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">These are not optional. The law is clear and <a href="https://liverpool.gov.uk/housing/landlords/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--navy);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(26,58,92,0.25);">Liverpool City Council</a> actively enforces compliance.</p>

